data.description: Coastal retreat home awaits in quiet neighborhood! Mesmerizing orange-glowed sunset views flood through the wall of windows, accentuated by the grand vaulted ceiling and timber beam accents. This incredibly designed 3 bedroom, 3 bath home sits just a few minute stroll to the salt water dip toes & walk the sandy beach. Relax & entertain on expansive back deck, plumbed for gas BBQ & equipped with hot/cold water. Stay comfortable year round with A/C, heat pump and cozy fireplace. Make the .37 acres your own with so many options: garden, a Mother-in-law suite, shop or perhaps build your dream backyard oasis w/an outdoor kitchen. This community enjoys and plays at their own Sandy Point's golf course, pool, clubhouse & marina. It's a lifestyle!
